SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t0].[c], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[c0]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT @__daydate_1 AS [c], [d].[Id], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], CASE
        WHEN (([t].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c0], [d].[CategoriesId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t0].[Id]

SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t0].[c], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[c0]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT @__daydate_1 AS [c], [d].[Id], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], CASE
        WHEN (([t].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c0], [d].[CategoriesId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t0].[Id]

FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT @__daydate_1 AS [c], [d].[Id], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], CASE
        WHEN (([t].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c0], [d].[CategoriesId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)

    (SELECT *
     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]
         WHERE [ep].[major_id] = [o].[object_id]
             AND [ep].[minor_id] = 0
             AND [ep].[class] = 1
             AND [ep].[name] = N'microsoft_database_tools_support'
    )
)
SELECT 1 ELSE SELECT 0

SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t0].[c], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[c0]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT @__daydate_1 AS [c], [d].[Id], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], CASE
        WHEN (([t].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c0], [d].[CategoriesId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t0].[Id]

FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT @__daydate_1 AS [c], [d].[Id], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], CASE
        WHEN (([t].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c0], [d].[CategoriesId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)

SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t0].[c], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[c0]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT @__daydate_1 AS [c], [d].[Id], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], CASE
        WHEN (([t].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c0], [d].[CategoriesId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t0].[Id]

SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t0].[c], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[c0]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT @__daydate_1 AS [c], [d].[Id], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], CASE
        WHEN (([t].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c0], [d].[CategoriesId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t0].[Id]

SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t0].[c], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[c0]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT @__daydate_1 AS [c], [d].[Id], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], CASE
        WHEN (([t].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c0], [d].[CategoriesId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t0].[Id]

     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]
         WHERE [ep].[major_id] = [o].[object_id]
             AND [ep].[minor_id] = 0
             AND [ep].[class] = 1
             AND [ep].[name] = N'microsoft_database_tools_support'
    )
)
SELECT 1 ELSE SELECT 0

SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t0].[c], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[c0]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT @__daydate_1 AS [c], [d].[Id], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], CASE
        WHEN (([t].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c0], [d].[CategoriesId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t0].[Id]

SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t0].[c], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[c0]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT @__daydate_1 AS [c], [d].[Id], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], CASE
        WHEN (([t].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c0], [d].[CategoriesId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t0].[Id]

    SELECT @__daydate_1 AS [c], [d].[Id], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], CASE
        WHEN (([t].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c0], [d].[CategoriesId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t0].[Id]

SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t0].[c], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[c0]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT @__daydate_1 AS [c], [d].[Id], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], CASE
        WHEN (([t].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c0], [d].[CategoriesId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t0].[Id]

LEFT JOIN (

        WHEN (([t].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c0], [d].[CategoriesId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    LEFT JOIN (

        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]

LEFT JOIN (

        WHEN (([t].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c0], [d].[CategoriesId]

        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]

SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t0].[c], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[c0]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT @__daydate_1 AS [c], [d].[Id], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], CASE
        WHEN (([t].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c0], [d].[CategoriesId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t0].[Id]

SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t0].[c], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[c0]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT @__daydate_1 AS [c], [d].[Id], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], CASE
        WHEN (([t].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c0], [d].[CategoriesId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t0].[Id]

SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t0].[c], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[c0]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT @__daydate_1 AS [c], [d].[Id], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], CASE
        WHEN (([t].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c0], [d].[CategoriesId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t0].[Id]

FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT @__daydate_1 AS [c], [d].[Id], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], CASE
        WHEN (([t].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c0], [d].[CategoriesId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)

) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[CategoriesId]

SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t0].[c], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[c0]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT @__daydate_1 AS [c], [d].[Id], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], CASE
        WHEN (([t].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c0], [d].[CategoriesId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t0].[Id]

     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'

         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]

             AND [ep].[minor_id] = 0

             AND [ep].[name] = N'microsoft_database_tools_support'
    )
)

2019-10-09 11:40:54.287 +03:00 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[@__daydate_1='?' (DbType = Date), @__companyid_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__userId_2='?' (Size = 450)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Name], [t1].[c], [t1].[PictureId], [t1].[CategoriesId], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Date], [u].[DishId], [u].[CompanyId], [u].[Quantity]
        FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]

        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Date], [u].[DishId], [u].[CompanyId], [u].[Quantity]
        FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]

SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Name], [t1].[c], [t1].[PictureId], [t1].[CategoriesId], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Date], [u].[DishId], [u].[CompanyId], [u].[Quantity]
        FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]

SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t0].[c], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[c0]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT @__daydate_1 AS [c], [d].[Id], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], CASE
        WHEN (([t].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c0], [d].[CategoriesId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t0].[Id]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT @__daydate_1 AS [c], [d].[Id], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], CASE
        WHEN (([t].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c0], [d].[CategoriesId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    LEFT JOIN (

        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]

    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[CategoriesId]

        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)

    SELECT @__daydate_1 AS [c], [d].[Id], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], CASE
        WHEN (([t].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c0], [d].[CategoriesId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t0].[Id]

         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]

             AND [ep].[name] = N'microsoft_database_tools_support'
    )

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Date], [u].[DishId], [u].[CompanyId], [u].[Quantity]
        FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]

        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]

2019-10-09 11:44:53.602 +03:00 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[@__daydate_1='?' (DbType = Date), @__companyid_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__userId_2='?' (Size = 450)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Name], [t1].[c], [t1].[PictureId], [t1].[CategoriesId], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Date], [u].[DishId], [u].[CompanyId], [u].[Quantity]
        FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]

        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Date], [u].[DishId], [u].[CompanyId], [u].[Quantity]
        FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]
2019-10-09 11:44:53.677 +03:00 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[@__daydate_1='?' (DbType = Date), @__companyid_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__userId_2='?' (Size = 450)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Name], [t1].[c], [t1].[PictureId], [t1].[CategoriesId], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Date], [u].[DishId], [u].[CompanyId], [u].[Quantity]
        FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]

2019-10-09 11:44:58.690 +03:00 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[@__daydate_1='?' (DbType = Date), @__companyid_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__userId_2='?' (Size = 450)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Name], [t1].[c], [t1].[PictureId], [t1].[CategoriesId], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]

    INNER JOIN (

        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]

        WHEN (([t].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c0], [d].[CategoriesId]

        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]

SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Name], [t1].[c], [t1].[PictureId], [t1].[CategoriesId], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Date], [u].[DishId], [u].[CompanyId], [u].[Quantity]
        FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]

        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]

FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]

        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    LEFT JOIN (

        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]

2019-10-09 11:46:57.593 +03:00 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[@__daydate_1='?' (DbType = Date), @__companyid_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__userId_2='?' (Size = 450)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Name], [t1].[c], [t1].[PictureId], [t1].[CategoriesId], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Date], [u].[DishId], [u].[CompanyId], [u].[Quantity]
        FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]

FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Date], [u].[DishId], [u].[CompanyId], [u].[Quantity]
        FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]

) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]

        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Date], [u].[DishId], [u].[CompanyId], [u].[Quantity]
        FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]
2019-10-09 11:52:38.211 +03:00 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[@__daydate_1='?' (DbType = Date), @__companyid_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__userId_2='?' (Size = 450)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Name], [t1].[c], [t1].[PictureId], [t1].[CategoriesId], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Date], [u].[DishId], [u].[CompanyId], [u].[Quantity]
        FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]

SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Name], [t1].[c], [t1].[PictureId], [t1].[CategoriesId], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Date], [u].[DishId], [u].[CompanyId], [u].[Quantity]
        FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]

        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]

) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]

        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
